ed qualitative scenario implies\nthat the main foreground effect of most clusters is $not$ always the expected\nSZ effect. This may be the reason why the SZ signal detection result is lower\nthan expected from the model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Nov 2012 04:37:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Mar 2013 01:43:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 6 May 2013 07:59:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-15"}
